To create a i386 library on OS X, in the sources directory : 

gcc -c -O3 -arch i386 *.c
ar cqs liblinebreak.a *.o
rm *.o

To create a i386 library on Linux, in the sources directory :

gcc -c -O3 -m32 *.c
ar cqs liblinebreak.a *.o
rm *.o

To create a 64bit library on Linux, in the sources directory :

gcc -c -O3 -m64 *.c
ar cqs liblinebreak.a *.o
rm *.o

